*Bolnice* su mesta gde se izvršavaju medicinske usluge i gde se pruža pomoć pacijentima. (Hospitals are places where medical services are performed and where help is provided to patients.)

U *bolnice* se često odlazi u slučaju prehlade ili zbog neke druge bolesti. (People often go to hospitals in case of a cold or some other illness.)

U *bolnice* se dolazi i zbog pregleda rutinskog karaktera. (People also go to hospitals for routine check-ups.)

U *bolnice* su smešteni pacijenti sa različitim dijagnozama. (Patients with various diagnoses are accommodated in hospitals.)

U *bolnice* se obavljaju operacije i druge vrste medicinskih intervencija. (Operations and other types of medical interventions are performed in hospitals.)